text: Edifício Altino Arantes is a skyscraper in São Paulo, Brazil. It is 161 meters (528 feet) tall and has 36 floors. It was built in 1947. ==Related pages== * Downtown São Paulo * Mirante do Vale * Edifício Itália ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in São Paulo Category:Skyscrapers in Brazil Category:Art Deco buildings Category:1947 establishments in South America Category:1940s establishments in Brazil
